name: Fantasy Eyes LORA
description:
Hello this is my LORA for beautiful detailed gemlike eyes! trained on 16 images of eye focus close-ups over AnythingV3 so works over most of the anime style models.

Recomended use 0.7 - 0.9.

use tag: ffyy , ypu can also increase intensity 1.1 or similar to improve effect

Some recommended tags (dont use many or it will give only one eye close up):

close-up, eye focus, tears, looking at viewer, eyelashes, thick eyebrows, thick eyelashes
